# st/

Steel threads are self-contained units of work, each implementing a specific piece of functionality or improvement. This directory organizes both completed threads (in COMPLETED/) and planned threads awaiting resources (in NOT-STARTED/), plus active work directories like ST0034/.

## Dirs

- `COMPLETED/` -- Finished steel threads (ST0001–ST0033, with some gaps)
- `NOT-STARTED/` -- Planned steel threads awaiting work initiation
- `ST0034/` -- Agentic Software Engineering Suite (v2.9.0 target; 12 WPs)

## Files

- `steel_threads.md` -- Master index tracking all steel threads by ID, slug, status, and dates
